                </div>
                <!--//icon-->
                <div class="content">
                    <h3 class="title">SITEMAP IN SECONDS</h3>
                    <p>Jump from vague ideas to a concrete plan with just a few clicks. Every time you plan a website, WriteMaps helps you to stay 100% focused on the planning, and not lose time on formatting.</p>
                </div>
